spec_data.Name: perl-Data-Page-Pageset
spec_data.Description:
Pages number can be very high, and it is not comfortable to show user from
the first page to the last page list. Sometimes we need split the page list
into some sets to shorten the page list.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:23:51 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Change long page list to be shorter and well navigate
